Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme song playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,TACTICS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[car engine idling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,DECEMBER 20, 11:50 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Raye Penber] You there?\N-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, I came to Japan\Nas a part of a secret investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so the local police can't find out that…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… That I'm…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise, I won't tell anyone\Nthat I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, that includes my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] Well then… Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I don't want the police to know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've come into contact\Nwith an FBI agent either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If my father ever found out,\Nthere's no doubt he'd let L know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that he doesn't suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for the police…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll treat this\Nas just another unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber sighs] What a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Raye, what's the matter?\NSomething happened, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard you sigh like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The bus I was on\Ngot hijacked, if you can believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A bus-jacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Some junkie robbed a bank\Ntwo days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I guess he wanted to try\Ntaking on a bus today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think this kind of thing\Nhappened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you were already riding the bus\Nwhen the hijacker got on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end, the guy freaked out,\Njumped off the bus and got hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] Did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't really stick around\Nto see what happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Naomi] You know… [sighs]\N-[Penber] Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little hard to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that that was all a coincidence,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You got on that bus because\Nyou were investigating someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're telling me\Nthat this criminal is most likely dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Doesn’t that suggest that you--\N-[Penber] That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. darling, you and I know you used\Nto be one of the best agents in the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you're my fiancée, Naomi.\NWe talked about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not an agent anymore,\Nso just leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't get involved\Nwith the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And you wouldn't do anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you promised\Nwhen we decided
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd come with me,\Nso I could meet your parents in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You do remember that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just force of habit.\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] No… I should be sorry.\NLet's forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, once we have a few kids\Nrunning around,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll probably be so busy\Nyou'll forget you were ever an agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mind will be occupied\Nwith better things too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,tell me how I can convince your dad\NI'm worthy of his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira doesn't scare me\Nhalf as much as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Oh, let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're about to write down\Nthe name of that agent, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-The one from the bus.\N-Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna wait one week\Nbefore writing his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If he dies right after meeting me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only draw attention to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write his name in here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,once I've given him time to investigate\Nmore people with ties to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be less obvious that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll use some of these inmates\NI've been keeping alive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to play around with L a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Watari] L.\N-[L] Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Another victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This one left\Nwhat appears to be a suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Please, send it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[computer beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gods of Death."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"L, do you know?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gods of Death"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he trying to tell us\Nthat Gods of Death exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the police to monitor\Nprison populations closely
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira may use other suicide notes\Nto communicate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,DECEMBER 27, 3:00 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] This place is crawling with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna do it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say\Nyou're about to see the results
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of all the research and experiments\NI've been doing over the last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] "Experiments"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been using known criminals\Nwho live in this part of town
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to test out different killing methods
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've learned a lot\Nabout the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,ACCIDENTAL DEATH, DECEMBER 26, 8:30 PM\NDIES AFTER GETTING HIT BY A CAR
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, if I write a cause of death\Nand the circumstances leading up to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can add a name afterwards\Nand it'll still happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,SHO HANEKURODA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Oh… even I didn't know that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Raye Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-I am Kira.\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Don't turn around\Nor put your hands in your pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hesitate to kill you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] It-- It couldn't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This voice…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, I'm gonna prove to you\Nthat I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see the man\Nworking over there at the coffee shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The one sweeping the floor.\NI'm gonna kill him just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But-- But… how?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping, grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I had no choice\Nbut to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured if I didn't kill\Nat least one person,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Although that man has been repeatedly\Ncharged with sexual assault,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,he's managed to avoid conviction\Nevery time due to lack of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a menace to society.\NHe got what he deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only assume\Nthat L has already informed you of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't kill someone who I haven't seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to know their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can easily kill all these people\Nright now, if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and choose someone\Nif you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] D-- Don't do it. I believe you.\NYou're Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you care more\Nabout your loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,than any of these people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine how you'd feel\Nif one of them was killed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,just because you refused to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should consider them\Nthe real hostages at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem surprised.\NI've been investigating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't do exactly as I say,\Nshe will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so will the rest of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Including you.\NAnd that's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- I understand.\NJust tell me what you need me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've got your laptop with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the files containing the identities\Nof all the FBI agents who came to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] I do have my laptop with me.\NIt's the one I use for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have the files\Nyou're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] All right.\NThen take this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Penber] Huh?\N-[envelope rustles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,First, take the transceiver\Nout of the envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and put the earpiece in\Nand await my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] A transceiver.\NThis thing looks like a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But there'll be no record\Nof this transmission anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it allows us to converse\Nfrom a close distance, even underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He really thought this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] All right.\NNow get on the Yamanote Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Inner or outer route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nwhich direction you take.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,SHIBUYA - SHINAGAWA\N15:10
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be close by at all times,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which means I'll be watching\Nyour every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get on the train,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,pick a spot in front of you\Nand don't take your eyes of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see you looking around,\NI will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've boarded, I want you\Nto take the seat closest to the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's occupied, wait until it's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[train horn blares]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm going to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have even the slightest suspicion\Nthat you're not being honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,your girlfriend is as good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How many FBI agents\Nare currently in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak quietly into the transceiver\Nand don't make it obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it's four teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Three agents per team\Nfor a total of 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Okay. Now, take the papers\Nout of the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] What… is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of those 12 agents you mentioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to write down\Nthe name of your superior,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who is heading up\Nthis investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in the space at the very top of the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] What is the meaning of this?\NWhat is he after?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's face it,\Nhe hasn't really left me any choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's not like he can kill them\Nusing just their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, take out your laptop and turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Any minute now your boss\Nis going to send you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,a message with a file attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It contains the names and photos\Nof all the FBI agents
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,currently active in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] But-- This… This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Now, one by one\Nyou’re going to look at each photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and then write that agent's name\Nin the space provided.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to do this for each agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's got the names already\Nwhy use me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he planning to do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Good. Looks like you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, put the transceiver\Nand all the papers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,back into the original envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and place them on the rack\Ndirectly above your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,After that,\Nyou're going to stay in your seat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and ride the train\Nfor at least another 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When you are absolutely certain\Nthat nobody will notice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you leaving without the envelope,\Nyou can get off of the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Penber] I know that voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on earth can't I remember\Nwho it belongs to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira… who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[loud heartbeat]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping, groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[train doors hiss]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Light… Yagami…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Raye Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Raye Penber wrote all of those names\Non pages taken from the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Without even realizing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,he was actually signing a death warrant\Nfor all of his colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Penber's boss…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,he died of a heart attack\Nafter sending all of his agents a file.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other 11 investigators…\N[chuckles lightly]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,…they all died of heart attacks\Nafter receiving the same file.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] L… You have a call\Nfrom the Director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[FBI Director] It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a report\Nin front of me right now stating
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that all of our agents in Japan\Nare dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All 12 died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only assume\Nthat Kira is behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm sorry, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're calling off our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] I have Chief Yagami on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] L, I've just got off the phone\Nwith the Director of the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,According to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems that you arranged for the FBI\Nto come to Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and investigate everyone here\Nassociated with the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] So, how do you explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we now suspects\Nin our own investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I felt that it was necessary\Nto uncover Kira's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] I cannot accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it unbelievable\Nthat you would spy on us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the very people working with you\Non this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I knew all along\Nwe couldn't trust that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\NKira killed those FBI agents, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious he'll kill anyone\Nwho gets in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether they are criminals or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for his sense of justice.\NHe's a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] We have another victim.\NA note was found at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,L, do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gods of Death…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] …love apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Raye's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he was…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was murdered by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu] Um, so… what's\Nwith the family meeting, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you're going\Nto find out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I might as well tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to be alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've heard\Nof this Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am currently in charge of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's totally awesome, Dad.\NYou're the best cop ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] That's not quite the point\NI'm trying to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the truth is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the FBI sent 12 of their agents to Japan\Nto assist us in finding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of them… died yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Does that mean they were killed by Kira?\N-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a chance that Kira\Nwill actually try to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone who comes after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,His crimes are ruthless
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and more frightening\Nthan anything we've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Many detectives have already quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you should quit too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to die!\NWhat if he gets you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sachiko] That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is so much more important\Nthan some job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never forgive myself\Nif I walked away from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not sit back and let evil triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Dad, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, dear…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's honorable of you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud to be able\Nto call you my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And if anything should ever happen to you,\NI'm going to find Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and make sure he gets executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] We now know\Nthat Kira doesn't just target criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll kill anyone who opposes him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite possible\Nthat we may all be killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of your own lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,your families, and all the others\Nyou'd be leaving behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone wants\Nto leave this investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be demoted\Nif you choose not to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're not absolutely sure\Nthen we don't need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be willing\Nto fight against him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,even if that means\Nmaking the ultimate sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[officer 1] So… what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[officer 2] I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[driver] Oh, yeah. That' him, all right.\NThere's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember him\Nbecause he told us to get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't really remember\Nany of the other passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for talking with me, anyway.\NI appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit of a long shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But if what I'm thinking is right…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira could have been\None of the passengers on the bus that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that is the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,then I know that he is close enough\Nto use this bus route.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,SERIAL MURDER\NSPECIAL INVESTIGATIONS HQ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Five men, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, six including myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm grateful to see
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's as many as five of you\Nwilling to risk your lives to face evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] The fact that you've chosen to stay\Nmeans you have a strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-I trust all of you.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hol-- Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,L just said\Nthat he's decided to trust us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But honestly, what reason\Ndo we have to trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, L, all of us have agreed\Nto put our lives at risk
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring Kira to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I hope you understand\Nwhat this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really sticking our necks out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] But you never have to\Nshow your face, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You just give the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see how you can expect us\Nto work alongside you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,under those conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If all of us are going to work together\Non this investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you truly meant what you said\Nabout trusting the six of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,could you come here,\Nso we can all meet in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] The thought had\Nalready crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I did say\Nthat I trusted all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, keep what is about to happen\Na secret between the eight of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to meet the six of you\Nwhom I trust as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, I want you all to go\Noutside of the police building
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and decide once more\Nif you trust me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,NATIONAL POLICE AGENCY AND\NNATIONAL PUBLIC SAFETY COMMISSION
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ukita] Why is he seeking our help now?\NThere's only six of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He solved all of these difficult cases\Nby himself in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what makes this one so different?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They way L's been\Nconducting things so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,odds are he's gonna send a stand-in\Nor a proxy of some kind to meet us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of coming himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we'd ever know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A proxy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] I believe L.\NI think we can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really see how we can\Nsolve this case without his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning\Nhe's been very upfront about the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that he'd need the help of the police\Non this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we should think of it like…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,he's been waiting for this to happen\Nall along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a number of people\Non the task force
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who distrusted L\Nbefore this investigation began.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And once we got started,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we had detectives\Nresigning left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Following that\Nclassified information was leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm not surprised\Nthat he didn't trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, he was waiting\Nfor the task force to get narrowed down
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to only those investigators\Nhe could trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,he needed to weed out anyone\Nwho wasn't totally committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're working with that guy,\NI'm leaving the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't try to follow you,\NI'm not interested in finding L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think we can trust L,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'd be willing to cooperate with him\Non this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I am staying in a suite\Nat the Teito Hotel at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll be switching hotels\Nevery few days
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,from this point on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to think of these hotel rooms\Nas the de facto
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,headquarters of this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[elevator dings]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If this arrangement\Nis acceptable to all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then split into two groups
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and stagger your arrival,\Nso you come 30 minutes apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, arrange it\Nso you're all here at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems we're getting\Ncloser to each other in equal steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time\Nbefore we collide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to show my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make my first public appearance as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever manage to find out\Nabout these secret meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'd feel compelled to move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm counting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I've been quite active\Nover these last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Think carefully.\NWas there anything I missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What comes next?\NThere are endless possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The real battle\Nis only just beginning now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] It's unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let yourselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[music playing]